What's the secret?

18:47.041 --> 18:51.481
Since I retired, I've found some new
hobbies: golf, fishing, personal Pilates.

18:52.961 --> 18:54.601
And a few old ones.

18:57.081 --> 19:01.201
But not a word to Ingeborg.
OK, let's get down to business.

19:03.081 --> 19:04.641
Creation, production...

19:05.041 --> 19:07.921
You get the other half when
the movie's finished. OK.

19:10.281 --> 19:12.321
OK, time for a sherry.

19:13.721 --> 19:16.681
The film team is the best in the region.

19:17.321 --> 19:18.601
Here they are!

19:20.001 --> 19:21.681
Come in, guys.

19:23.041 --> 19:24.041
Hi, Lukas.

19:24.481 --> 19:27.401
Hi there, y'all!
We're the team from...

19:27.641 --> 19:29.841
French Fried Fur Films Ltd. Inc.,

19:30.241 --> 19:34.201
your cinematic service
from wedding vows to wedding night.

19:34.441 --> 19:37.961
My esteemed colleague Lukas
is a master cinematographer.

19:38.681 --> 19:41.561
And I'm Adam, the go-to guy
if good's not enough

19:41.921 --> 19:44.961
and you want excellent...
- Tone it down.

19:45.321 --> 19:49.281
Lukas. Bückstedt, pleased to meet you.
My wife Dietlinde.

19:49.921 --> 19:51.921
Bückstedt and Knackstedt,

19:52.721 --> 19:54.761
the perfect match, huh?

19:58.081 --> 19:59.881
Are you famous?

20:00.401 --> 20:03.081
I could swear I've seen you before.

20:04.481 --> 20:07.601
I've run the Wild Mouse rollercoaster
in Hamburg for 35 years.

20:08.481 --> 20:11.601
