on the high striker.

20:12.041 --> 20:13.641
The rollercoaster man!

20:13.881 --> 20:14.881
Please!

20:15.081 --> 20:18.281
Do it just once.
I'm a great admirer of your art.

20:18.721 --> 20:21.081
Dad...
- Please! Just once!

20:24.081 --> 20:25.961
Step right up, folks!

20:26.321 --> 20:29.601
Climb aboard for a ride
that'll knock your socks off!

20:29.841 --> 20:31.641
Here we go now!

20:33.681 --> 20:36.321
Thaaaaaat's right!

20:36.561 --> 20:40.521
Can you take any more, folks?
The worst is yet to come!

20:44.081 --> 20:47.561
If you want to win, win, win,
go next door, you wimps!

20:47.801 --> 20:51.841
This here is the Wiiiiiiiiiild Mouse!

20:52.201 --> 20:55.241
Step right up, folks!
Don't be shy now!

20:55.601 --> 20:59.481
Scratch your balls, stroke your pussies,
buy a ticket, don't be wussies!

20:59.841 --> 21:03.961
Huge tits, wet piss flaps,
you'll end up puking on your laps!

21:12.241 --> 21:15.561
Ingeborg, stop making such a fuss!

21:17.401 --> 21:18.961
Unbelievable!

21:19.961 --> 21:23.201
Oh, Ingeborg!
- And you can cut that out!

21:25.481 --> 21:28.641
We're ready.
- I can't do it, Lukas!

21:29.561 --> 21:33.601
The fact that those carnies are marrying
into our family is driving me crazy.

21:33.961 --> 21:38.161
I wish I could say something brilliant,
but I don't know them any better than you.

21:38.961 --> 21:42.281
But I know Mila,
and I know that Martin loves her.

21:42.841 --> 21:45.201
His other girlfriends
were a weird bunch.

21:45.721 --> 21:49.441
Mary, Peggy, Nicki and Beate.

21:49.801 --> 21:51.441
Mary was the cop with great...

21:51.921 --> 21:55.321
With... Did breathalyzer
tests in a sexy cop uniform.

21:55.561 --> 21:57.681
You didn't like any of them.
Rightly so.

21:58.481 --> 22:01.801
Peggy thought sparrows were baby pigeons.

22:02.121 --> 22:06.321
And Nicki almost starved to death
trying to count the steps on an escalator.

22:07.161 --> 22:08.801
Nicki was a gas!

22:11.281 --> 22:12.641
Mila's different.

22:13.201 --> 22:17.041
And if someone manages to raise
such a sweet, loveable person,

22:17.281 --> 22:19.761
then they can't be so bad.

22:20.641 --> 22:22.401
Go on, give her a chance.

22:26.161 --> 22:29.121
And that's for not being born
30 years sooner.

22:35.481 --> 22:36.681
Women...

22:49.281 --> 22:51.041
And action!

22:52.001 --> 22:53.441
Heinz-Dieter...

22:53.721 --> 22:56.721
